text: Laurence Delasaux (born 31 March 1985) is a former English squash player. He achieved his highest career ranking of 65 on October 2010 during the 2010 PSA World Tour. Laurence moved to Toronto and became a coaching professional after retiring from international squash in 2012. == References == Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:English male squash players Category:Sportspeople from Kingston upon Hull
